<item>
            <title>[SOLR-6] Solr admin stylesheet doesn&apos;t work well with Internet Explorer</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-6</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The admin pages look different on firefox than on IE (6 or 7).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;tables in text analysis page span whole browser, regardless of cell size&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;separators visible in firefox aren&apos;t visible in IE&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</description>
